The Nollywood teenage actress, Regina Daniels (Christian faithful) which has been trending on social media space recently has been reportedly converted to Islam by his billionaire husband who has four other wives which includes a Muslim from Morocco. Ned Nwoko whose muslim name is Munir was alleged to have converted the teenage actress and named her Fatima just after the news of her pregnancy went viral, according to the information from the insider. The reason for the denouncement of her Christian faith is connected to the fact that she will be relocated to London where she would have her baby and the billionaire husband wants her hooked to the tenets of Islam There are reports that the teen actress is four months pregnant for her billionaire husband. Source: tori.ng